title: Let's Talk - Dad/Daughter Q & A Series - Part 3

media:group.media:title: Let's Talk - Dad/Daughter Q & A Series - Part 3
media:group.media:description: Dad, do you and your daughter LAUGH together? This week Drs. Ken and Michelle continue their series for dads of daughters with a light-hearted topic. Shared laughter is a great way to bond with your daughter, and there are deeper benefits as well.
